      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute gem! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car that it still feels like it\u2019s brand new. It\u2019s in truly mint condition\u2014sparkling clean inside and out, and it drives like a dream. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and it shows! Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
