    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in high-revving, naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M-differential lock. The chassis is superlative, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a complete bushings refresh to maintain factory kinematics. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components. With original paint depth and a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle offers a tactile driving experience defined by precise throttle response and optimal corner-exit traction.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
