      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine example of automotive excellence, meticulously maintained by a single owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, showroom luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating, showing no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats are firm and unmarked, the dashboard is free of any UV damage, and it still carries that fresh, new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is flawless, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Every button, sensor, and feature functions perfectly. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the driver who demands nothing less than perfection. Includes all original manuals, two key fobs, and the original window sticker.",
